# SECURITY: Never hardcode credentials in application.properties
# All secrets (MAIL_PASSWORD, MONGO_URI, etc.) must only be set
# as Environment Variables in Render dashboard — never in source code.
# Reference them in application.properties as: ${ENV_VAR_NAME} with NO fallback value.